template = Template(
    """
        ${a()}
        <%def name="a()">
            <%def name="b()">
                <%def name="c()">
                    comp c
                </%def>
                ${c()}
            </%def>
            ${b()}
        </%def>
"""
    )
eq_(flatten_result(template.render()), 'comp c')
